# Settings Components Export Fix

## Problem
Browser error: `The requested module '/src/components/settings/SettingsCard.tsx' does not provide an export named 'SettingsCard'`

The barrel export file `src/components/settings/index.ts` was importing components as named exports, but the component files were only exporting as default exports.

## Root Cause
Mismatch between import and export patterns:
- **index.ts** (barrel file): `export { SettingsCard } from './SettingsCard'` (named export)
- **SettingsCard.tsx**: `export default SettingsCard` (default export only)

## Solution
Added named exports to all settings components while maintaining backward-compatible default exports:

```tsx
// Before
export default SettingsCard;

// After
export { SettingsCard };
export default SettingsCard;
```

